    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A compact marble of brilliant red color blotched with white and found in Montagne Noir and other regions in the Pyrenees. Resembles griotte marble.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
